            <h1>The economy</h1>
            <div class="temaMobIngressImg" style="display: none;"><img src="/Upload/PORTAL/Temabilder/okonomi_150x113.jpg" alt="The scales of economy" /></div>
            <p class="textIngress">The Government’s goals for its economic policy are full employment, sustainable development, a more just system of distribution and a strengthening of the welfare system. The different elements of the policy shall together ensure that these goals are achieved.</p>
            <img src="/Upload/PORTAL/Temabilder/okonomi_150x113.jpg" alt="The scales of economy" class="temaIngressImg" />
            <div class="descriptionText"><p>In the Government, it is <em>the Minister of Finance’s</em> responsibility to draw up and coordinate economic policy. <em>The Ministry of Finance</em> acts as the secretariat for the Minister of Finance. It is the political authorities - the Government and the Storting – that make the decisions. On this page you will find general information and documents relating to the economy. </p>
<p>You can explore this topic in more detail by using the menu on the right.</p></div>
